data.description: Back on market at no fault of sellers. This is also an assumable VA loan with 3.875%. This 7 bed 4 and half bath, three story home, is the epitome of premier elegance in the heart of Evans Georgia. This home boasts a luxurious owner's suite on main. Pride in ownership is obvious in this home. European inspired exterior, extensive mill work package, hardwoods, granite kitchen, island, gas stove, and gourmet double oven. Tiled owner's bath with HUGE owner's closet and separate sitting area with fireplace in owner's suite. Loft consists of an additional master and two additional bedrooms with a sizable laundry room. Third floor includes a dramatic media room and two bedrooms sharing the full bath. The flat rear yard is an oasis featuring a large gazebo. The rear patio is screened and enclosed with tile floors. This home is perfect for large gatherings and would make an exceptional Master's rental. Crawford Creek Subdivision offers walking trails, sidewalks, street lights, two pools, clubhouse, pickleball, and basketball court. This home is occupied
